{"tid":2056432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（九國聯軍）捷克宣告加入「跨國議會聯盟」聯手對抗中共","createTime":"2020-06-08T16:21:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T12:59:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":72,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e27620004e05f2bb4b3629c6ed74b5a4fd73de2e","tid":2056432,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:21:17.000Z","msg":"面對中共威脅，美、英、日等八個國家的國會議員和政要，上週五宣布成立「對華政策跨國議會聯盟」，聯手應對中共挑戰。週一，捷克共和國議員宣布，加入聯盟。<br />\n<br />\n上週五「對華政策跨國議會聯盟」宣布成立，共包括美、英、日、澳、德等8個國家。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦共和黨參議員 Marco Rubio﹕「中共統治下的中國，為全球帶來挑戰。」<br />\n<br />\n歐洲議會議員 Miriam Lexmann﹕「這是一個將會定義未來整個世紀的挑戰。」<br />\n<br />\n德國國會基民黨議員 Michael Brand﹕「這個挑戰，將會影響我們所有人。」<br />\n<br />\n週一，捷克共和國議員也宣告加入。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/06/08/a102866089.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2Fa102866089.html&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19vY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=251754df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/06/08/a102866089.html</a>"},{"pid":"27317de0591d4434b672b20ad96e88627690ef19","tid":2056432,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:21:45.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"1bd601f728d8da7b573432763756da354cdb1833","tid":2056432,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:23:03.000Z","msg":"中國強大了,起碼要十六國聯軍先夠face"},{"pid":"39d93825de992ca87bd437f189f2f7bd20dd2e42","tid":2056432,"uid":214192,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:23:25.000Z","msg":"要多啲政要加入先有大作用<br />\n每個國家得一兩個議員可以做嘅野有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9698981aa45a6417bc363acae73128cde6d223f0","tid":2056432,"uid":198866,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:27:04.000Z","msg":"有德國喎，奶共又要食兩邊茶禮"},{"pid":"f74be7771adfc059bc35a8aab232cc7ebd1c3891","tid":2056432,"uid":225798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1bd601f728d8da7b573432